  topicTitleText: {fileID: 72716699}
  topicContentText: {fileID: 72716698}
  exitButtonCanvas: {fileID: 5889248795865102975}
  availableTopics:
  - title: Food Culture in Malaysia
    content: '"Why Malaysian food is loved locally and internationally." Talk about
      famous dishes like nasi lemak, roti canai, and laksa. Discuss the influence
      of Malay, Chinese, and Indian cuisines. Mention how food brings people together
      during festivals.'
  - title: The Importance of Exercise
    content: '"How regular movement keeps the body and mind healthy."

      Explain
      physical benefits like strength and endurance.

      Discuss mental health
      benefits. Suggest fun, accessible exercise types.'
  - title: Time Management for Students
    content: "\u201CHow planning and prioritizing helps balance studies, hobbies,
      and social life. Discuss tools like calendars or apps. Explore common challenges
      like procrastination.\u201D"
  - title: Public Transportation Improvements
    content: '"How transport is changing in Malaysian cities." Discuss MRT, LRT,
      and bus expansions. Mention how better transport helps reduce traffic jams.
      Talk about the shift towards electric buses and greener options.'
  - title: Technology in Everyday Life
    content: '"How modern devices change the way we live and work." Talk about smartphones,
      AI, and smart homes. Discuss pros and cons of technology. Mention how tech
      affects communication.'
  - title: 'Healthy Eating Habits '
    content: '"How balanced diets and good food choices improve health."  Discuss
      the importance of fruits, vegetables, and whole grains.  Explore how reducing
      sugar and processed foods impacts energy levels.  Mention cultural differences
      in diet.'
  - title: Hobbies and Free Time
    content: "\u201CHow hobbies improve creativity and reduce stress. Discuss different
      types of hobbies like sports, arts, or gaming. Explore how hobbies differ across
      cultures.\u201D"
  - title: Dream Jobs and Careers
    content: "\u201CHow people imagine their future careers. Discuss skills needed
      for different jobs. Explore how culture and education influence career choices.\u201D"
  - title: Festivals and Celebrations
    content: "\u201CHow cultural festivals bring people together. Discuss examples
      like Chinese New Year, Diwali, or Christmas. Explore the meaning of traditions.\u201D"
